WEBVTT

00:00:28.355 --> 00:00:30.332
Nazvao ga je "X element".

00:00:30.356 --> 00:00:31.546
(Smeh)

00:00:31.570 --> 00:00:34.198
I rekao je, "Preimenovaćemo
mi taj X malo kasnije."

00:00:34.927 --> 00:00:38.070
I onda, 10 godina kasnije,

00:00:38.094 --> 00:00:40.093
u priču ulazi jedna američka naučnica,

00:00:40.117 --> 00:00:42.498
koja opet koristi mikroskop da gleda

00:00:42.522 --> 00:00:44.355
ćelije insekata.

00:00:44.887 --> 00:00:46.283
I vidi nešto neobično.

00:00:46.307 --> 00:00:48.429
Ima još tog tamnog materijala.

00:00:48.453 --> 00:00:49.609
Nekako je sićušan,

00:00:49.633 --> 00:00:52.545
i nalazi se pored X elementa.

00:00:52.569 --> 00:00:54.141
Na kraju je neko rekao,

00:00:54.165 --> 00:00:55.899
"Ako se ovaj prvi zove X,

00:00:55.923 --> 00:00:58.121
zašto ne bismo ovaj drugi nazvali Y?"

00:00:58.145 --> 00:00:59.684
I tako (pucketa prstima)

00:00:59.708 --> 00:01:01.739
su otkriveni polni hromozomi.